ğŸ“‰ Key Terms
Intercept (bâ‚€): Value of Y when all X = 0

Coefficient (bâ‚, bâ‚‚...): Effect of each feature on the target

Random State: Ensures reproducible splits

Seed: Controls randomness in shuffling/training

Dummy Variable Trap: Occurs when all dummy variables are used â€” remove one

